natspec.details: Handles "phantom overflow" i.e., allows multiplication and division where an intermediate value overflows 256 bits
natspec.notice: Facilitates multiplication and division that can have overflow of an intermediate value without any loss of precision
natspec.title: Contains 512-bit math functions
